text:
An extension of Scarlett supermarket located a level above.

Some products are repetitive of the bigger store, plush toys are now found only at this store.

One of the multiple Chinese supermarket within the People's Park Complex. I found some of the items that I usually bought from Scarlett Mart to be cheaper here but then I found that they are from Scarlett as well. What a diversification!

The peaches I bought were moldy and rotten, and a piece of each one was squashed. The same thing happened to the green grapes I bought last time. The inside part of the grapes was wilted and yellow. Deliberately hiding the stale areas...
